		</Group>
		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="440" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">矩阵变换出数个折射镜，在领域不断发射并弹射激光，持续造成<span color="#bababa">50%,25%,<br/>12.5%,5%</span><span>伤害，最后发射两束激光持续造成</span><span color="#bababa">50%,5%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="447" width="424" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">矩阵拼接出一个力场屏障并推出，不断推开玩家，接触持续造成<span color="#bababa">40%,20%,10%,4%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="671" width="426" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">矩阵在前方汇聚蓄力电磁激光，约4s后发射激光，造成<span color="#bababa">70%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="895" width="439" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">矩阵在形成激光发射器，标记瞄准玩家，发射激光持续造成<span color="#bababa">70%,35%,<br/>17.5%,7%</span><span>伤害，激光方向是从玩家左侧到右侧的一个圆弧。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="1343" width="424" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" textDecoration ="underline" color="#ffffff">垂降部件<span textDecoration="none">周期性朝玩家位置进行下落攻击，造成</span><span textDecoration="none" color="#bababa">50%</span><span textDecoration="none">伤害；两个垂降部件之间若距离较近，则产生连线，持续造成</span><span textDecoration="none" color="#bababa">20%,10%,5%</span><span textDecoration="none">伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1599" width="408" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" textDecoration ="underline" color="#ffffff">电锯部件<span textDecoration="none">周期性朝玩家位置快速移动，持续5s，持续造成</span><span textDecoration="none" color="#bababa">50%,25</span><span textDecoration="none" color="#b8b8b8">%</span><span textDecoration="none">伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="1599" width="408" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" textDecoration ="underline" color="#ffffff">激光部件<span textDecoration="none">周期性朝玩家位置发射激光，造成</span><span textDecoration="none" color="#bababa">50%</span><span textDecoration="none">伤害，有穿透性。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1119" width="1005" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">矩阵游离出<span textDecoration="underline" color="#ccffbf">一对电锯部件和激光部件(A)</span><span>、或者</span><span textDecoration="underline" color="#ccffbf">一对锥针和激光部件(B)</span><span>，进入「不可视」状态，清除自身所有元素附着，所有抗性提升</span><span color="#ffbfbf">200%</span><span>，持续60s。对本体使用</span><span color="#8affc5">激化</span><span>反应或使用雷元素攻击</span><span textDecoration="underline">修复中部件</span><span>即可破除该状态。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="671" width="411" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">矩阵蓄力发射大枚锥子，约3s后丢出，造成<span color="#bababa">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="895" width="437" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">矩阵在累计进入隐蔽状态大于1min后，此时会同时修复6个部件，并在约10s后产生超频冲击，造成<span color="#bababa">100%</span><span>伤害，使用</span><span color="#ffacff">雷元素</span><span>命中部件会瘫痪矩阵10s。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="447" width="429" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">矩阵架起镜阵，投射12道激光，每个造成<span color="#b9b9b9">50%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
